orce microscopy\nimages. The method of molecular dynamics allowed us to establish the structures\nof SWNT:PSE:GOX created in the aqueous environment and to determine the\ninteraction energy between hybrid components. In addition, the conductivity of\nthe SWNT network with adsorbed PSE and GOX molecules is studied.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 14 Aug 2012 11:52:56 GMT"}],"update_date":"2012-08-15"}
